snippet.title: Blips a sokoban style game with exploding dynamite based on dos bips released for vircon32
snippet.description:
Blips for #vircon32 is a #remake of the dos bips #game made by Bryant Brownell, its a #sokoban style #puzzle game but with exploding dynamite and collecting coins
